## 4. Typography

### Display Font: Barlow Condensed

Self-hosted WOFF2 files. Weights: 700 (Bold), 800 (ExtraBold), 900 (Black). Loaded with `font-display: swap` for performance.

| Token | Value | Usage |
|-------|-------|-------|
| `--inv-font-display` | `'Barlow Condensed', Impact, 'Arial Narrow', sans-serif` | Hero headlines, section titles, price callouts |

- Always uppercase. Always condensed. Tight tracking (`-0.02em`). Tight leading (`1.1`).
- Never use Barlow Condensed for body text, navigation, UI labels, or any text smaller than 18px.
- Weights 800 and 900 are preferred for hero headlines. Weight 700 for section titles.

### Body Font: Shopify Theme Font

The body font is configured through Shopify theme settings and referenced via `--font-body-family`. The Invicta token aliases it for consistency.

| Token | Value | Usage |
|-------|-------|-------|
| `--inv-font-body` | `var(--font-body-family)` | All body text, descriptions, UI labels, navigation |

- Sentence case for all body text. Normal tracking (`0`). Normal leading (`1.5`).
- Never override the body font with a hardcoded `font-family` declaration.

### Type Scale

