### Easing Functions

| Token | Value | Usage |
|-------|-------|-------|
| `--inv-ease-default` | `ease` | Standard easing for most transitions |
| `--inv-ease-out-slow` | `cubic-bezier(0, 0, 0.3, 1)` | Natural deceleration, drawer slides |
