### Animation Rules

- All animations must respect `prefers-reduced-motion`. The theme already has 22+ media queries for this. New animations must include a reduced-motion override.
- Hover states: `--inv-duration-fast` (100ms). Drawer slides: `--inv-duration-moderate` (200ms). Page transitions: `--inv-duration-slow` (300ms).
- No decorative animations. Every animation must communicate a state change (hover, open/close, loading, success/error).
- The bounce easing is reserved for the cart count badge and similar micro-feedback. Do not use it on large elements.

