The z-index hierarchy is fixed. No values outside this scale are permitted. If a new layer is needed, add it to the token file between existing values.

| Token | Value | Usage |
|-------|-------|-------|
| `--inv-z-base` | `0` | Default stacking context |
| `--inv-z-dropdown` | `100` | Dropdown menus, tooltips |
