| `--inv-z-header` | `999` | Site header |
| `--inv-z-overlay` | `1000` | Background overlays, scrims |
| `--inv-z-drawer` | `2000` | Cart drawer, mobile nav drawer |
| `--inv-z-search-dropdown` | `9999` | Search results dropdown |
| `--inv-z-modal` | `10000` | Modal dialogs |
| `--inv-z-search-active` | `99999` | Active search overlay |
| `--inv-z-toast` | `100000` | Toast notifications (highest) |

- Never use arbitrary z-index values (`z-index: 50`, `z-index: 5000`, etc.). Always reference `--inv-z-*` tokens.
- If two elements need different stacking within the same tier, use stacking context isolation (`position: relative; z-index: 0`) rather than inventing new z-index values.

