## 9. Component Patterns

### Hero (invicta-hero-v3)

- Dark `#2D2D2D` background, full-bleed width.
- Two-column layout: text content left, product image right.
- Red eyebrow tag (small uppercase label above headline).
- Barlow Condensed uppercase headline, 54px desktop / 40px tablet / 28px mobile.
- Description text at 16px, opacity 0.7 for subtle legibility on dark backgrounds.
- Two CTAs: primary (red background, white text) + secondary (outline, white border/text).
- Background texture via `::before` pseudo-element. Bottom accent line via `::after`.
- Product image: 380px max, clean on transparent/dark background, right-aligned.
- Optional price callout badge on the product image.

### Product Card (invicta-product-card v7.7)

- White card (`#FFFFFF`) on the grey page background (`#F5F5F6`).
- Sharp corners (`--inv-radius-card: 0`). Subtle shadow (`--inv-shadow-card`).
- 1:1 aspect ratio image container.
- Brand pill badge (rounded, brand-coloured background).
- Dual pricing: VAT-inclusive (primary) and ex-VAT (secondary), toggled by site-wide VAT switch.
- Compare-at price with percentage saving when on sale.
- Quick-add button.
- Trust indicators: stock status and delivery estimate.
- Supplier source tags control stock display (`invicta-stock`, `toolbank-stock`, `trend-stock`, etc.).

### Trust Elements

- Trust bar (`invicta-trust-bar` v2.0): horizontal strip with red accent icons. Five items: Authorised Dealer, Free Delivery, Full Warranty, Two Locations, Years Trading.
- Compact variant for product pages, full variant for cart and footer areas.
- Free delivery bar with progress indicator toward threshold.
- Delivery estimate component with next-day cutoff logic.

### Buttons

- **Primary:** red `#E11D26` background, white text, sharp corners, uppercase. Hover: `#B91C1C`.
- **Secondary:** dark `#2D2D2D` background, white text, sharp corners. Hover: `#404040`.
- **Outline:** transparent background, dark border (`#2D2D2D`), dark text. Hover: dark fill, white text.
- All buttons: 44px minimum height (touch target), no border-radius, font-weight bold.

### Forms

- Sharp corners on all inputs (`--inv-radius-input: 0`).
- Clear label-input association via `<label for="">` on every field.
- Error states use the `--inv-error` colour system (red border, light red background, red text).
- Focus states: 2px ring in `--inv-focus-ring-color` with 2px offset.

### Navigation

- Header v6.0: Mobile layout is hamburger + logo | search | VAT toggle + cart. Desktop: logo left | search centre | VAT toggle + account + cart right.
- Sticky header with slim profile on scroll.
- Nav colours: white background (`#FFFFFF`), text `#444444`, hover/active state uses accent red.
- Nav tokens: `--inv-nav-bg`, `--inv-nav-fg`, `--inv-nav-hover-fg`, `--inv-nav-active-fg`, `--inv-nav-border`, `--inv-nav-indicator`.

