## 10. Photography & Imagery

- Product images: clean white background, consistent lighting, no lifestyle props. The product is the subject.
- Hero images: product on transparent or dark background, placed on the right side of the hero layout.
- Brand logos: all supplied as SVG. Use monochrome (dark on light, or white on dark) where possible for consistency.
- No stock photography. No lifestyle shots of people holding tools unless from Invicta's own photo shoots.
- All product images should be square (1:1 aspect ratio) for grid consistency.
- Image alt text must be meaningful and specific: "DeWalt DCD776 18V Combi Drill" not just "Drill" or the product title repeated.

